{"settings":"{
  "[config]": {
    "editor.defaultFormatter": "foxundermoon.shell-format"
  },
  "[dotenv]": {
    "editor.defaultFormatter": "foxundermoon.shell-format"
  },
  "[ignore]": {
    "editor.defaultFormatter": "foxundermoon.shell-format"
  },
  "[properties]": {
    "editor.defaultFormatter": "foxundermoon.shell-format"
  },
  "[scminput]": {
    "editor.rulers": [
      {
        "color": "#34D39955",
        "column": 50
      },
      {
        "color": "#60A5FA55",
        "column": 72
      },
      {
        "color": "#F8717155",
        "column": 80
      }
    ],
    "editor.wordWrap": "off"
  },
  "[shellscript]": {
    "editor.defaultFormatter": "foxundermoon.shell-format"
  },
  "accessibility.verbosity.inlineChat": false,
  "better-comments.tags": [
    {
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "bold": false,
      "color": "#f87171",
      "italic": false,
      "strikethrough": false,
      "tag": "!",
      "underline": false
    },
    {
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "bold": false,
      "color": "#e0af68",
      "italic": true,
      "strikethrough": false,
      "tag": ":",
      "underline": false
    },
    {
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "bold": false,
      "color": "#60A5FA",
      "italic": false,
      "strikethrough": false,
      "tag": "?",
      "underline": false
    },
    {
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "bold": true,
      "color": "#f472b6",
      "italic": false,
      "strikethrough": false,
      "tag": ".",
      "underline": false
    },
    {
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "bold": false,
      "color": "#fb923c",
      "italic": false,
      "strikethrough": false,
      "tag": "todo",
      "underline": false
    },
    {
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "bold": false,
      "color": "#4ade80",
      "italic": false,
      "strikethrough": false,
      "tag": "*",
      "underline": false
    },
    {
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "bold": true,
      "color": "#c084fc",
      "italic": false,
      "strikethrough": false,
      "tag": "+",
      "underline": false
    }
  ],
  "chat.editor.fontSize": 14,
  "chat.editor.wordWrap": "on",
  "code-runner.enableAppInsights": false,
  "code-runner.ignoreSelection": true,
  "code-runner.saveFileBeforeRun": true,
  "codestats.apikey": "SFMyNTY.ZEhCemRHVmphQT09IyNNakEzTXpJPQ.GfcHPCbWC70BtlKK7t_GgD31clhncDSbEasD53-tkDI",
  "codestats.username": "tpstech",
  "cSpell.customDictionaries": {
    "custom-dictionary-user": {
      "addWords": true,
      "name": "custom-dictionary-user",
      "path": "~/.config/.cspell/custom-dictionary-user.txt",
      "scope": "user"
    }
  },
  "cSpell.dictionaries": [
    "typescript",
    "typescript_ts",
    "html",
    "css",
    "json",
    "markdown",
    "en-au"
  ],
  "cSpell.enabled": true,
  "cSpell.language": "en-AU",
  "cSpell.showAutocompleteSuggestions": true,
  "cSpell.suggestionMenuType": "quickFix",
  "css.completion.completePropertyWithSemicolon": true,
  "css.lint.duplicateProperties": "warning",
  "css.lint.unknownAtRules": "ignore",
  "debug.autoExpandLazyVariables": true,
  "debug.console.fontSize": 16,
  "debug.inlineValues": "on",
  "debug.terminal.clearBeforeReusing": false,
  "debug.toolBarLocation": "floating",
  "diffEditor.codeLens": true,
  "diffEditor.experimental.showMoves": true,
  "editor.accessibilitySupport": "off",
  "editor.bracketPairColorization.enabled": true,
  "editor.codeActionsOnSave": {
    "source.addMissingImports": "explicit",
    "source.organizeImports": "explicit"
  },
  "editor.fontFamily": "'MesloLGM Nerd Font Mono', 'RobotoMono Nerd Font', 'FiraMono Nerd Font'",
  "editor.fontLigatures": true,
  "editor.fontSize": 16,
  "editor.formatOnSave": true,
  "editor.guides.bracketPairs": true,
  "editor.guides.bracketPairsHorizontal": true,
  "editor.guides.highlightActiveIndentation": "always",
  "editor.inlineSuggest.enabled": true,
  "editor.linkedEditing": true,
  "editor.minimap.maxColumn": 80,
  "editor.minimap.size": "fit",
  "editor.quickSuggestions": {
    "comments": "inline",
    "other": "on",
    "strings": "on"
  },
  "editor.renderLineHighlight": "gutter",
  "editor.renderWhitespace": "boundary",
  "editor.rulers": [
    {
      "color": "#34D39955",
      "column": 80
    },
    {
      "color": "#60A5FA55",
      "column": 100
    },
    {
      "color": "#F8717155",
      "column": 120
    }
  ],
  "editor.semanticHighlighting.enabled": true,
  "editor.snippetSuggestions": "top",
  "editor.suggest.shareSuggestSelections": true,
  "editor.suggestSelection": "first",
  "editor.tabSize": 2,
  "editor.wordWrap": "on",
  "emmet.includeLanguages": {
    "astro": "html",
    "postcss": "css",
    "svelte": "html",
    "vue": "html"
  },
  "explorer.compactFolders": false,
  "explorer.confirmDelete": false,
  "explorer.confirmDragAndDrop": false,
  "explorer.openEditors.visible": 1,
  "git.autofetch": true,
  "git.confirmSync": false,
  "git.followTagsWhenSync": true,
  "git.suggestSmartCommit": false,
  "github.copilot.chat.welcomeMessage": "never",
  "github.copilot.editor.enableCodeActions": true,
  "github.copilot.enable": {
    "*": true
  },
  "github.gitAuthentication": true,
  "github.gitProtocol": "ssh",
  "githubPullRequests.assignCreated": "${user}",
  "githubPullRequests.defaultMergeMethod": "squash",
  "grammarly.config.documentDialect": "australian",
  "grammarly.config.documentDomain": "business",
  "grammarly.config.suggestionCategories.prepositionAtTheEndOfSentence": "on",
  "grammarly.config.suggestionCategories.stylisticFragments": "on",
  "grammarly.config.suggestionCategories.unnecessaryEllipses": "on",
  "inlineChat.mode": "preview",
  "markdown.preview.fontFamily": "'Helvetica Neue', -apple-system, 'Segoe WPC', sans-serif",
  "markdown.preview.fontSize": 16,
  "markdown.preview.lineHeight": 1.2,
  "scm.inputMinLineCount": 36,
  "terminal.integrated.cursorStyle": "line",
  "terminal.integrated.env.osx": {
    "CW_NEW_SESSION": "1",
    "Q_NEW_SESSION": "1"
  },
  "terminal.integrated.fontFamily": "'MesloLGM Nerd Font Mono', 'Helvetica Neue'",
  "terminal.integrated.fontSize": 14,
  "terminal.integrated.shellIntegration.suggestEnabled": true,
  "window.title": "${activeEditorShort}${separator}${activeRepositoryName} / ${activeRepositoryBranchName}",
  "workbench.colorTheme": "Tokyo Night tpsTech Inspired Teal",
  "workbench.editor.enablePreview": false,
  "workbench.editor.enablePreviewFromQuickOpen": true,
  "workbench.editor.highlightModifiedTabs": true,
  "workbench.editor.tabActionLocation": "left",
  "workbench.editor.tabSizing": "fixed",
  "workbench.iconTheme": "material-icon-theme",
  "workbench.tree.indent": 16,
  "workbench.tree.renderIndentGuides": "always"
}"}
